    <briefdescription>
<para>Data structure containing the version of the firmware running on the watch. The version of the firmware has the form X.[X.[X]]. If a version number is not present it will be 0. For example: the version numbers of 2.4.1 are 2, 4, and 1. The version numbers of 2.4 are 2, 4, and 0. </para>
    </briefdescription>
